": "action_item", "extraction_text": "I'll send out the calendar invite after this call.", "char_interval": {"start_pos": 842, "end_pos": 892}, "alignment_status": "match_exact", "extraction_index": 15, "group_index": 14, "description": null, "attributes": {"owner": "Marcus", "deadline": "after this call"}}, {"extraction_class": "topic", "extraction_text": "finalize the Q4 numbers", "char_interval": {"start_pos": 817, "end_pos": 840}, "alignment_status": "match_fuzzy", "extraction_index": 16, "group_index": 15, "description": null, "attributes": {"importance": "high"}}], "text": "Marcus: Alright, let's look at the Q3 overages. Julia, the ad spend was about 15% higher than we projected in August.\r\nJulia: Right, that was for the late-summer campaign. We saw a high conversion rate, but I agree we need to tighten it up for Q4. I’ll pull the full conversion report by Wednesday so we can see if that extra spend actually paid off.\r\nMarcus: That would be helpful. Sam, how are we looking on the new software licenses?\r\nSam: We’re still waiting on the final quote from the vendor. They promised it by end of day today. Once I have that, I’ll send it over to you, Marcus, for approval.\r\nMarcus: Perfect. I also need someone to update the master budget spreadsheet with these new figures.\r\nJulia: I can take care of that once I finish the report.\r\nMarcus: Thanks, Julia. Let’s meet again on Friday to finalize the Q4 numbers. I'll send out the calendar invite after this call.", "document_id": "doc_3121df67"}
